\id 2TH Kharam: Bible Translation 1st Edition. 
\h 2 Thessalonia 
\toc1 THESSALONIA Mi-ngaidiang Paul Inni Huuina Chemajia 
\toc2 2 Thessalonia 
\toc3 2 Thes 
\mt1 THESSALONIA 
\mt2 Mi-ngaidiang Paul Inni Huuina Chemajia 
\imt1 Chonglamsaat 
\ip 2 Thessalonia hi tirton paul in imajia eii (1:1). \bk 1 Thessalonia amajiasuo nuk-ah apha sootlek leiya Paul in 2 Thessalonia hi Jisu Christa inneisuo kum soomra-nga leikhat pheiweiya imajia eii. \bk*Hiwa larik amajia phahin Paul hi Corinth khan alaleiom. Hiwa larik hi Paul in woini huuina Pathian chuonkatho (missionary) asina lamma iphun Thessalonica koisuok diang imajia eii (Chuon 17:1-10). Tirton ngai Chuontho larik khan hiwa koisuok hi Jihudi lekkhat li Greek mi katamtak inchunliya inbool koisuok eii tiya aril. 
\ip Thessalonia koisuok mi ngai'n aheknasi nikhuo khat-um Christa juokirnasik jarra inthiarra inleijetzoot jarra Paul in 1 Thessalonia khat-um 2 Thessalonia larik hin hiwa jarra katamkhat amajia. 2 Thessalonia larik hin katamkhat chu ahekna nikhuo jarra Paul in tam amajia. Tirton Paul in hiwa larik hin akadool kha emaru takkha mi rakip in inwon sipnasik chuon kathokha eru tia chongthakna um anei (3:6-10). 
\iot Asuungnga kaom Chong 
\io1 1. Paul apumtak khat-um achuon thopui mi ngaikha malarna anei \ior (1:1-2)\ior* 
\io1 2. Hiwa thengli Paul in Thessalonica koisuok ngaikha Pathian diang aminpaak halli Pathian diang nipina anei \ior (1:3-12)\ior* 
\io1 3. Paul in ahekna nikhuo jarra rilna anei \ior (2:1-17)\ior* 
\io1 4. Paul in akadool emaru takkha chuon kangar eru tiya rilna anei \ior (3:1-15)\ior* 
\io1 5. Insuona Chong \ior (3:16-18)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Paul, Silas khat-um Timothy, 
\p Thessalonica ah kaom nipa Pathian khat-um Pumi Jisu Christa mi ka-eii koisuok ngaidiang: \rq Chuon 17:1\rq* 
\p  
\v 2 Nipa Pathian khat-um Pumi Jisu Christa diangnga inphut nangni chungnga riangwai khat-um kahoi kadai kha omrase. 
\s1 Christa Juoni Chongtan 
\p  
\v 3 Ule naingai, eini'n apha rakip-ah nangnisik bit-ah Pathian niminpaaksik eii. Ajarchu hiwahi eini'n thosik-ah rahoi suok, ajarchu nangni ngamna kha hong-insoon halli nangni rakip in inkhatli inkhat ning-inriang kha-um ahonglok.  
\v 4 Khawa jarra keini kinpum tak-in Pathian koisuokngai diang nangni jarra in-orna kinnei. Nangni'n ningtongpui poongraalna rakip-ah ningdei khat-um ngamna ningcheet jarra um in-orna kinnei. 
\p  
\v 5 Hiwa rakip ngai'n Pathian chongtan khachu adik tia amalar, nangni'n ningpoong khan ajar-eya Pathian rengram sik-ah nangni rahoi ning-eii.  
\v 6 Pathian chu akadik kha eii: nangni kanaminpoong ngaikha ama'n aminpoongsik eii,  
\v 7 halli ama'n keini poongna khat-um nangni poongna kha anakhaipisik eii. Hiwahi ama'n Pumi Jisu kha marwaan makheiya ranak kangar ama marwaan tirton ngaikha mei machuon le inruoiya ajuoni khan,  
\v 8 Pathian kajetmak khat-um Pumi Jisu chongkahoi kajuimak mi ngai khachu ama'n mei le inruoiya arachaak sik eii. 
\p  
\v 9 Inmani khachu Pumi makheiya inlaak khat-um ama lurna lianna ranak makheiya inlaak kumsoot mangna kha inmusik eii, \rq Isa 2:10\rq* 
\p  
\v 10 ama mi rakip diang lurna lianna khat-um ama ka-ngamna rakip diang khoya kaleisik-ah ajuo Nikhuo nikhan, nangni um inmani karra ning-inchelsik eii ajarchu nangnidiang kinril chongpui kha nangni'n ngamna ningneijei. 
\p  
\v 11 Khawa jarra keini'n nangni sik-ah inchat lekleiya Pathian diang kinni. Pathian nakoina ringkhuo khan nangni'n rahoi ka-eya ningring matornasik keini'n Pathian diang kinnanipi. Nangni i-ngaidon akatha rakip khat-um nangni ngamna kaom chuon ngaikha ama ranak khan huui namintungpi erase.  
\v 12 Hinthoa Eini Pumi Jisu raming kha nangni diangnga inphut lurna lianna kha amusik eii, halli eini Pathian khat-um Pumi Jisu Christa riangwai jarra inphut nangni'n lurna lianna kha amadiang makheiya ningmusik eii. 
\c 2  
\s1 Manu Mi 
\p  
\v 1 Eini Pumi Jisu Christa akajuosik halli eini'n amadiang ni-inchunsik jarra, kei'n ule nai nangnidiang hiwa ngaihi kanaminthozoot, \rq 1 Thes 4:15-17\rq* 
\p  
\v 2 khachu ratha-ah erase, chongpuiya erase, emakli keini imajia chongnga erase, Pumi Nikhuo kha ajuojei iti chongkhan nangni innottheiya ningmalung mindongmaru khat-um ningka-iit kha emaru.  
\v 3 Tuteii innum maleisei thoa nangni kha ang rakip-ah lamleiitiang inruoimaru. Ajarchu ahekna kathamak pha heiwa masa makleiseng halli meikhurra kaluutsik Manu Mi kha inlarmasa maklaiseng khawa Nikhuo kha heiwanuni. 
\p  
\v 4 Ama'n chubei thosik ah rahoi ka-eii Pathian emakli phur rakip kha zootnuni halli apum takkha hiwangai rakip chungnga inchoisaang. Ama'n sita Pathian biak-inn khannum in-ongta Pathian ka eii atisik eii. \rq Dan 11:36; Ezek 28:2\rq* 
\p  
\v 5 Nangni'n ngaidonmakchu bejei? Kei'n nangnile kalei omlai hiwangai rakip hi nangnidiang kei'n kaleiriljei.  
\v 6 Hiwahi tuun laminsuok maknasik ook-ah kaom inkhat om halli khawa kha nangni'n ningjetjei, apha chei tinikhan Manu Mi kha inlarsik eii.  
\v 7 Inthup ah kaom Manu Mi ranak kha tuun chuon athoa omjei, takkha tuun aka-ook ama kha lam makheiya inkhaimaklaiseng akasuoksik kha lasuoknuni. 
\p  
\v 8 Halli khawapha khanchu Manu Mi kha malarsik ejei, takkha Pumi Jisu ajuoni khan, Manu Mi kha Pumi mur makheiya aphuksaan ranakkhan ama kha athatsik eii halli Pumi ra-aang khan Manu Mi kha aminmangsik eii. \rq Isa 11:4\rq* 
\p  
\v 9 Manu Mi khan Seitan ranak-ah heiwata kadikmak inlakchuon khat-um ngak kaom angjet ngaikha athosik eii, \rq Matt 24:24\rq* 
\p  
\v 10 halli Pathian kajetmak kamangnga kaom mi ngaidiang rilkacha maleisei angjet arilsik eii. Inmani ngaikha inthisik eii ajarchu ringna sik-ah akadikkha inmalungnga keiluutmu.  
\v 11 Hiwa jarra inmani'n akadikmak kha ngamnarasu tia Pathian in akadikmak ranak kha inmani diang chuon katho sik-ah ijuotir eii.  
\v 12 Ajuotirna ajarchu akadik kha kangamnamak, takkha akathamak kamanuom mi rakip kha minmangnasik eii. 
\s1 Sanminringna sik-ah nangni Inakadang eii 
\p  
\v 13 Pumi'n inaminriang ule naingai, nangni sik bit-ah keini'n inchatlekleiya Pathian minpaaksik rahoi eii. Ajarchu Pathian'n nangni kha sanminringna sik-ah Ratha ranak-ah khat-um akadik kha ningngamna jarra ama sik-ah inthiang mi ngai namin-enasik mansakhet-ah\f + \fr 2:13. \fq mansakhet; \ft manuscript lekkhat achu \fqa inphutna makheiya tia injia.\f* inakadang kha ning-ejei.  
\v 14 Eini Pumi Jisu Christa lurna lianna khan tum ningchang nasik-ah, Pathian'n nangnikha keini'n kinril chongkahoi khan inakoi kha eii.  
\v 15 Khawa jarra, ule naingai, kacheet-ah ngirru halli kinmurra kinril emakli kinmajia chongnga keini'n nangnidiang kinnaminchu akadik ngaikha kacheet-ah mahuumru. 
\p  
\v 16 Eini kanaminriang halli ama riangwai khan masokna khat-um ngamna kacheet kanapeii eini Pumi Jisu Christa khat-um nipa Pathian in  
\v 17 nangnikha kumsoot akatha katho khat-um akadik karil ning-enasik bit-ah nasongpui khat-um na-ngirpui kha erase. 
\c 3  
\s1 Keini sik Pathian diang Nanipiru 
\p  
\v 1 Ahekna khet-ah, ule naingai, nangni diang aleikasuok kha angnga, Pumi chongkahoi hi innottheiya khat-um kalurra inkeiluut nasik-ah keini sik-ah Pathian diang nanipiru.  
\v 2 Pathian in keini hi manu khat-um akathamak mi ngai diangnga inphut anasan nasik-um Pathian nanipiru, ajarchu mi rakip in chongkahoi hi ka-ngamna emu. 
\p  
\v 3 Takkha Pumi chu ngamna kaom eii, halli ama'n nangni kha anamin-ngarsik khat-um Seitan diangnga inphut anasansik eii.  
\v 4 Keini'n Pumi diang nangni jarra ngamna kinnei, khachu nangni'n ningtho khat-um nangnidiang thoru kinti ngaikha thochei ningte tiya kinlei. 
\p  
\v 5 Pathian minriangna khat-um Christa in poongraal ideikha incheen doomma ningjetnasik Pumi'n nangni kha nanruoipui erase. 
\s1 Thosik Kasuok Chuon 
\p  
\v 6 Ule naingai, akadool ule nai khat-um keini naleipeii dan ngaikha akajuimak inmani rakip makheiya inphut kalaak-ak omru tia eini Pumi Jisu Christa ramingnga chongpeii hi nangnidiang kinda.  
\v 7 Nangni'n keini omchan ngaikha angtho tholia ningjutsikme tikha ningjetjei. Keini'n nangnile kinom laikhan eini akadool kha emakmi.  
\v 8 Keini'n tuteii bukha aman pelekleiya bakmung, takkha nangni tuteii diang-um phurrik emaknasik keini'n inchatlekleiya suunli zaan boiya chuon kintho.  
\v 9 Hiwa kinthona jarhi, keini'n nangni diang nasanru kinti nasik kinrei ommak jarra emak, takkha nangni juisik-ah abi inkhat kindazoot-ah kintho eii.  
\v 10 Keini'n nangnile kinlei omlai, keini'n nangni diang kinleiti kachak, “Chuon kathomak mi kha bak marase.” 
\p  
\v 11 Nangni karra chuon tholekleiya, chor intiya halkaom, akadool miring lekkhat inom tihi keini'n kinjet.  
\v 12 Khawa mi ngaidiang keini'n Pumi Jisu Christa ramingnga omchian inlang chuon tho-inlang ringnasik chuon thoru tia kinmasok khat-um chongpeii kinda. 
\p  
\v 13 Ule naingai, chuon katha katho sik kapoongkha emaru.  
\v 14 Hiwa chemajia larik hinna juisik-ah kinleida kajuimak miring lekkhat omthei eii, khawa mi ngaikha katha-ah jetru halli inmani ngaikha jakna inmunasik inmani khale inlopmaru.  
\v 15 Takkha inhalpui mit-enna inmani ngaikha enmaru; khawa rathuulla, ule nai mit-enna minchuru. 
\s1 Ahekna Chongda 
\p  
\v 16 Akahoi akadai thutbul, Pumi ama tak-in, chuon rakip-ah khat-um apha rakip-ah akahoi akadai kha inapeii erase. Pumi'n nangni rakip nanruoipuichak erase. 
\p  
\v 17 Kei'n hiwa inpaakna chonghi kakut tak-in kimajia kha eii. Kacheii majia rakip-ah Paul kei'n katia jetnabi kadeeng; hin thoa kei'n kamajia. 
\p  
\v 18 Eini Pumi Jisu Christa riangwai kha nangni rakip chungnga omrase.